OL,3,CEarly Easter adds to woe of retailers
OL,4,Csuffering from low consumer confidence
OL,6,FA survey for the bank found almost
OL,7,Fthree quarters of consumers (72%)
OL,8,Fexpect tension in the Middle East to
OL,9,Faffect the cost of living throughout
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,FSpending on travel fell 5.7% in April,
OL,13,Fafter a 3.3% drop in March, with
OL,14,Fspending on airlines down 8.3% as
OL,15,Fconsumers cited concerns about travel
OL,16,Fcosts (70%) and travel disruption
OL,17,F(62%) in light of the Middle East
OL,18,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
