PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778551406
OL,3,CEarly Easter adds to woe of retailers
OL,4,Csuffering from low consumer confidence
OL,6,FOne in six (16%) said they were
OL,7,Fputting off holiday decisions until
OL,8,Fthe outlook had stabilised.
OL,10,FJack Meaning, chief UK economist at
OL,11,FBarclays, said: "With uncertainty high
OL,12,Fboth at home and abroad, it is
OL,13,Funsurprising to see confidence
OL,14,Ffalling. The key unknown for the UK
OL,15,Foutlook is how long this uncertainty
OL,16,Fwill last.
OL,26,@sD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
