PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778551406
OL,3,CEarly Easter adds to woe of retailers
OL,4,Csuffering from low consumer confidence
OL,6,F"If confidence remains subdued for too
OL,7,Flong, and consumers continue to limit
OL,8,Ftheir spending as a result, it will be
OL,9,Fa challenge for households and
OL,10,Fbusinesses to weather the storm."
